  '10000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002',
  'The Legacy Builder',
  'legacy-builder',
  'Building a family compound, not buying a house. Every decision is measured in decades.',
  2,
  'Acquiring property as long-term family asset — compound or estate for multiple generations. Extended family input, trust/estate planning, focus on physical scale (lot size, expansion potential, privacy). Drawn to established prestigious communities with membership infrastructure and social continuity. Rarely sell, value scarcity and exclusivity as markers of long-term preservation.',
